      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJORS CREEK (5) finished in the money at Young two starts back then did a good job again at her latest appearance over 2170m at at this track, beaten 13 metres into third after being handy all the way. Won't find this any harder and she can take care of this line-up. ROCKET ME (8) has recorded two wins and two minor placings from the past five starts. Maintained the impressive form last time when 11 metres from the winner in third over 1720m at Young. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. This is a nice drop in grade so he is in the right race to find the winners' list. ULTIMATE ROCKER NZ (3) is worth another chance after a last-start ninth over 1730m at Bathurst five days ago. MODERN SHEEN (2) disappointed last time when seventh over 1740m at Riverina Paceway. Can do a lot better so worth considering.",
